### Restaurant Endpoints

### Get All Restaurants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/restaurants?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Restaurant by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/restaurants/restaurant-123
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Popular Restaurants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/restaurants/popular?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Nearby Restaurants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/restaurants/nearby?latitude=40.7128&longitude=-74.0060&radius=5&limit=20
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Search Restaurants
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/restaurants/search?query=pizza&limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Restaurants by Category
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/restaurants/category/italian?limit=20&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### Get Restaurant Menu
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/restaurants/restaurant-123/menu?limit=50&offset=0
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###